{"data":[{"name":"79:1","price":"誓以急掣的，","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰزِعَٰتِ غَرۡقٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5713,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:2","price":"轻曳的，","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰشِطَٰتِ نَشۡطٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5714,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:3","price":"奔驰的，","arabic":"وَٱلسَّٰبِحَٰتِ سَبۡحٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5715,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:4","price":"先驱的，","arabic":"فَٱلسَّٰبِقَٰتِ سَبۡقٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5716,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:5","price":"决策的，","arabic":"فَٱلۡمُدَبِّرَٰتِ أَمۡرٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5717,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:6","price":"当震动者震动，","arabic":"يَوۡمَ تَرۡجُفُ ٱلرَّاجِفَةُ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5718,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:7","price":"而续发者续发之日，","arabic":"تَتۡبَعُهَا ٱلرَّادِفَةُ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5719,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:8","price":"在那日，许多心将忐忑不安，","arabic":"قُلُوبٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ وَاجِفَةٌ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5720,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:9","price":"许多眼将不敢仰视。","arabic":"أَبۡصَٰرُهَا خَٰشِعَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5721,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:10","price":"他们说：我们必定复元吗？","arabic":"يَقُولُونَ أَءِنَّا لَمَرۡدُودُونَ فِي ٱلۡحَافِرَةِ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5722,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:11","price":"那是在我们已变成朽骨的时候吗？","arabic":"أَءِذَا كُنَّا عِظَٰمٗا نَّخِرَةٗ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5723,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:12","price":"他们说：然则，那是一次亏折的复原。","arabic":"قَالُواْ تِلۡكَ إِذٗا كَرَّةٌ خَاسِرَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5724,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:13","price":"那只是一次吼声，","arabic":"فَإِنَّمَا هِيَ زَجۡرَةٞ وَٰحِدَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5725,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:14","price":"他们忽然在地面之上。","arabic":"فَإِذَا هُم بِٱلسَّاهِرَةِ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5726,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:15","price":"穆萨的故事已来临你了吗？","arabic":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ مُوسَىٰٓ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5727,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:16","price":"当时，他的主，曾在圣谷杜洼中召唤他说：","arabic":"إِذۡ نَادَىٰهُ رَبُّهُۥ بِٱلۡوَادِ ٱلۡمُقَدَّسِ طُوًى","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5728,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:17","price":"“你到法老那里去吧！他确是悖逆的。","arabic":"ٱذۡهَبۡ إِلَىٰ فِرۡعَوۡنَ إِنَّهُۥ طَغَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5729,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:18","price":"你对他说：“你愿意成为纯洁的人吗？","arabic":"فَقُلۡ هَل لَّكَ إِلَىٰٓ أَن تَزَكَّىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5730,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:19","price":"你愿意我引导你认识你的主，而你敬畏他吗？”","arabic":"وَأَهۡدِيَكَ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَتَخۡشَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5731,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:20","price":"他把那最大的迹象昭示了法老，","arabic":"فَأَرَىٰهُ ٱلۡأٓيَةَ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5732,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:21","price":"但他否认，而且违抗。","arabic":"فَكَذَّبَ وَعَصَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5733,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:22","price":"然后转身而奔走。","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَدۡبَرَ يَسۡعَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5734,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:23","price":"于是，召集民众，而且喊叫，","arabic":"فَحَشَرَ فَنَادَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5735,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:24","price":"说：“我是你们至尊的主。”","arabic":"فَقَالَ أَنَا۠ رَبُّكُمُ ٱلۡأَعۡلَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5736,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:25","price":"故安拉以后世和今世的刑罚惩治他。","arabic":"فَأَخَذَهُ ٱللَّهُ نَكَالَ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةِ وَٱلۡأُولَىٰٓ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5737,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:26","price":"对于畏惧的人们，此中确有一种鉴戒。","arabic":"إِنَّ فِي ذَٰلِكَ لَعِبۡرَةٗ لِّمَن يَخۡشَىٰٓ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5738,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:27","price":"你们是更难造呢？还是天是更难造的呢？他曾建造了天，","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ أَشَدُّ خَلۡقًا أَمِ ٱلسَّمَآءُۚ بَنَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5739,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:28","price":"他升起它的高度，而成全它的形体，","arabic":"رَفَعَ سَمۡكَهَا فَسَوَّىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5740,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:29","price":"他使它的夜间黑暗，并显出它的光明。","arabic":"وَأَغۡطَشَ لَيۡلَهَا وَأَخۡرَجَ ضُحَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5741,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:30","price":"此后，他将地面展开，","arabic":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضَ بَعۡدَ ذَٰلِكَ دَحَىٰهَآ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5742,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:31","price":"他使地面涌出泉水来，生出植物来。","arabic":"أَخۡرَجَ مِنۡهَا مَآءَهَا وَمَرۡعَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5743,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:32","price":"他使山峦稳定，","arabic":"وَٱلۡجِبَالَ أَرۡسَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5744,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:33","price":"以便你们和你们的牲畜获得享受。","arabic":"مَتَٰعٗا لَّكُمۡ وَلِأَنۡعَٰمِكُمۡ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5745,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:34","price":"大难来临的时候，","arabic":"فَإِذَا جَآءَتِ ٱلطَّآمَّةُ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5746,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:35","price":"就是人将记起自己所作的善恶，","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَتَذَكَّرُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَا سَعَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5747,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:36","price":"火狱将为能见的人显露出来的日子。","arabic":"وَبُرِّزَتِ ٱلۡجَحِيمُ لِمَن يَرَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5748,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:37","price":"悖逆，","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَن طَغَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5749,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:38","price":"而且选择今世生活的人，","arabic":"وَءَاثَرَ ٱلۡحَيَوٰةَ ٱلدُّنۡيَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5750,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:39","price":"火狱必为他的归宿。","arabic":"فَإِنَّ ٱلۡجَحِيمَ هِيَ ٱلۡمَأۡوَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5751,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:40","price":"至于怕站在主的御前受审问，并戒除私欲的人，","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ خَافَ مَقَامَ رَبِّهِۦ وَنَهَى ٱلنَّفۡسَ عَنِ ٱلۡهَوَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5752,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:41","price":"乐园必为他的归宿。","arabic":"فَإِنَّ ٱلۡجَنَّةَ هِيَ ٱلۡمَأۡوَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5753,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:42","price":"他们问你复活时在什么时候实现，","arabic":"يَسۡـَٔلُونَكَ عَنِ ٱلسَّاعَةِ أَيَّانَ مُرۡسَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5754,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:43","price":"你怎能说明它呢？","arabic":"فِيمَ أَنتَ مِن ذِكۡرَىٰهَآ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5755,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:44","price":"惟有你的主能知它的究竟。","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ مُنتَهَىٰهَآ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5756,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:45","price":"你的警告只有裨於畏惧它的人，","arabic":"إِنَّمَآ أَنتَ مُنذِرُ مَن يَخۡشَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5757,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"79:46","price":"他们在见它的那日，好像在坟里只逗留过一朝或一夕。","arabic":"كَأَنَّهُمۡ يَوۡمَ يَرَوۡنَهَا لَمۡ يَلۡبَثُوٓاْ إِلَّا عَشِيَّةً أَوۡ ضُحَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5758,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"}],"chapter":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at","Chapter An-Nazi'at","Nazi'at","Surah Nazi'at","Chapter Nazi'at","An Nazi'at","Surah An Nazi'at","Chapter An Nazi'at","Surah 79","Chapter 79","Those Who Pull Out","النازعات"]}